(1048, 17, 1, 'What does it mean to \"identify the four early regions\"?', 'To guess their names.', 'To draw a picture of them.', 'To name and describe each of the four main historical areas of Nigeria.', 'To remember only one region.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 10:25:54'),
