(1057, 17, 1, 'What was Lokoja\'s historical role related to colonial administration?', 'It was a major trading port for traditional goods.', 'It was an early administrative center in the Northern Protectorate.', 'It was a military base only.', 'It was a place where no British people lived.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 10:25:54'),
