(1069, 17, 1, 'What does \"moral dilemma\" mean in a complex situation?', 'A difficult choice between two possible actions, where neither is clearly better or worse.', 'An easy choice between right and wrong.', 'A situation where it\'s clear what to do.', 'A situation with no choices.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 10:25:54'),
