(1215, 7, 2, 'Imagine you have a small amount of allowance money. How would you apply basic concepts of budgeting to use it wisely?', 'Spend it all on candy immediately.', 'Hide the money and forget about it.', 'Plan to save some money and spend the rest on something important you need.', 'Ask someone else to spend it for you.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 12:44:06'),
