(1705, 1, 2, 'When you stand still and face the flag during the national anthem, how does this action represent unity?', 'It shows you are tired', 'It means you like to sing', 'It shows that people are joining together in respect for their country', 'It is only a rule', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 13:59:08'),
(1706, 1, 2, 'The Nigerian Coat of Arms shows two horses. How do these symbols explain unity and values?', 'They mean horses are strong', 'They show a specific animal that is important to the country\'s history', 'They represent dignity and pride', 'They symbolize the northern and southern parts of the country united', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 13:59:08'),
(1707, 1, 2, 'Why is it important to learn the meaning of the Nigerian flag\'s colors? How does this help you understand its significance?', 'It makes the flag look pretty', 'It helps you remember the flag\'s colors', 'It connects you to the values and ideals the country stands for', 'It is only a picture', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 13:59:08'),
(1708, 1, 2, 'A problem-solving activity: \"How to make young children understand the importance of the national pledge.\" How would you apply your understanding of symbols?', 'Explain each line of the pledge and connect it to actions they can do for Nigeria', 'Tell them to just memorize it', 'Only make them say it loudly', 'Ignore its meaning', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 13:59:08'),
(1709, 1, 2, 'You see the Nigerian Coat of Arms on government buildings. How does this apply your understanding of symbols to real-life examples?', 'It means the building is old', 'It shows that the Coat of Arms is an official symbol of the Nigerian government and its authority', 'It is only for decoration', 'It means the building is important', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 13:59:08'),
(1710, 1, 3, 'Your class is discussing Civic Education. Which statement best evaluates why understanding your duties as a citizen is as important as knowing your rights?', 'Duties are only for adults.', 'Duties make life harder.', 'Knowing duties helps you be responsible and contribute to the community, while rights protect you.', 'Rights are more important than duties.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1711, 1, 3, 'If you were asked to create a simple plan for a child to participate in their community, what would be the most effective action step?', 'Stay at home all day', 'Only watch TV', 'Only talk about community problems', 'Help with a local clean-up or volunteer for a school event', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1712, 1, 3, 'Think about your rights and duties as citizens. If you had to design a \"Good Citizen\" badge, what would be the most important symbol to represent both rights and duties?', 'A symbol of open hands (giving and receiving), or a balanced scale (fairness)', 'A symbol of a single person only', 'A symbol of a closed fist', 'A symbol of only fun things', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1713, 1, 3, 'Your class is discussing components of Civic Education. Which statement best evaluates why understanding rights and duties is crucial for good citizens?', 'Rights are more important than duties.', 'Duties are only for adults.', 'Understanding both helps citizens be protected and also act responsibly for their community\'s well-being.', 'Civic Education is too hard.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1714, 1, 3, 'If you were asked to create a simple interactive activity for younger students about community values, what would be the most effective activity?', 'A game where everyone competes', 'An activity where students draw pictures of things they don\'t like', 'An activity where no one talks', 'An activity where students learn how to share and help each other, showing the value of kindness', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1715, 1, 3, 'Think about how components of Civic Education apply in daily life. If you had to design a \"Good Citizen\" role-play for your school, what would be the most important part of the scenario to highlight democratic practice?', 'Leaders telling everyone what to do', 'Students having no say in rules', 'Students discussing a school problem and then voting for the best solution', 'Only one student making all choices', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1716, 1, 3, 'Your class is discussing civic responsibilities. Which statement best evaluates why everyone\'s participation in civic duties is crucial for community well-being?', 'Only adults need to do civic duties.', 'One person\'s action doesn\'t matter.', 'Even small actions from many people add up to big improvements and a stronger community for all.', 'Civic duties are boring.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1717, 1, 3, 'If you were asked to create a simple classroom rule reflecting a civic responsibility, what would be the most effective rule?', 'Never share school supplies.', 'Always make noise during lessons.', 'Ignore school rules.', 'Clean up your own mess and help keep common areas tidy.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1718, 1, 3, 'Think about how participating in civic duties benefits the community. If you had to design a \"Community Helper\" project for younger students, what would be the most important task to demonstrate contribution?', 'To only read about community problems', 'To identify a local need (like a messy park) and work together to clean it up', 'To guess who caused problems', 'To only talk about helping', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1719, 1, 3, 'Your class is discussing national identity. Which statement best evaluates why unity in diversity is a great strength for Nigeria?', 'Diversity makes unity impossible.', 'Unity means everyone is the same.', 'When different groups respect each other, it makes Nigeria stronger and richer in culture.', 'Only one culture can be strong.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1720, 1, 3, 'If you were asked to create a new national symbol for Nigeria, what key idea would it emphasize?', 'Division among people', 'Everyone being same', 'Only one group being important', 'Strength through coming together, like different colors blending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1721, 1, 3, 'Think about how individuals contribute to national identity. If you had to design a \"Proud Nigerian\" activity for students, what would be the most important task to demonstrate their contribution?', 'To only read about Nigeria', 'To avoid national issues', 'To show how they respect national symbols and participate in community clean-ups', 'To only talk about themselves', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1722, 1, 3, 'Your class is discussing national identity. Which statement best evaluates why citizenship is key to a nation\'s strength?', 'Citizenship is only for leaders.', 'Citizenship means only following rules.', 'Knowing your rights and duties as a citizen helps you participate responsibly and build a strong nation.', 'Citizenship is not important.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1723, 1, 3, 'If you were asked to create a simple drawing for a new national symbol representing unity, what would be the most effective image?', 'A single, strong animal', 'Many different hands holding together', 'Only one color', 'A very tall building', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1724, 1, 3, 'Think about appreciating cultural diversity. If you had to design a \"National Identity\" activity for younger students, what would be the most important task to highlight diversity?', 'Asking them to only learn about one culture', 'Asking them to share a traditional song or dance from their own family\'s culture', 'Telling them to ignore differences', 'Making everyone dress the same', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1725, 1, 3, 'Your class is discussing patriotism. Which statement best evaluates why patriotism is crucial for national development?', 'Patriotism means being boastful.', 'Patriotism only helps leaders.', 'It inspires citizens to work together, obey laws, and contribute to the growth and progress of their country.', 'Development happens without patriotism.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1726, 1, 3, 'If you were asked to create a short play to teach younger students about patriotism, what key message would it emphasize?', 'Only famous people are patriotic.', 'Patriotism means ignoring problems.', 'Patriotism is about winning everything.', 'Loving your country means helping your community and following rules.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1727, 1, 3, 'Think about applying emotional intelligence in being a good patriot. If you had to design a \"Patriotism Pledge\" for your school, what emotion would it focus on for uniting students?', 'Anger at others', 'Fear of the future', 'Shared pride and love for Nigeria to encourage teamwork and kindness', 'Sadness for the country', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1728, 1, 3, 'Your class is discussing national symbols. Which statement best evaluates why a national symbol is crucial for representing a nation\'s values?', 'Symbols are just pictures.', 'Symbols only have one meaning.', 'They are visual tools that quickly tell people about a nation\'s history, beliefs, and shared identity.', 'Only some countries have symbols.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1729, 1, 3, 'If you were asked to create a new national symbol for Nigeria, what would be its main purpose?', 'To make people argue', 'To be very complicated', 'To be the biggest symbol', 'To represent unity, strength, or diversity of the nation', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1730, 1, 3, 'Think about the role of national symbols in representing unity. If you had to design a \"National Pride\" activity for your school, what would be the most effective way to help students appreciate national symbols?', 'Organize a display or presentation where students share the meaning and history of each national symbol', 'Ask them to ignore the symbols', 'Have students draw their own symbols that are different from national ones', 'Organize a quiz about the shapes of symbols', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:00:09'),
(1731, 21, 1, 'Which of these is one of the Nigerian ethnic groups mentioned in this lesson?', 'The American people', 'The French people', 'The Chinese people', 'The Bura people', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1732, 21, 1, 'What does \"ethnic group\" mean?', 'A group of people who share a common culture, language, or history', 'A group of people who only speak one language', 'A group of people who live in the same house', 'A group of people who only eat the same food', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1733, 21, 1, 'What is cultural diversity in Nigeria?', 'When everyone in Nigeria is exactly the same', 'When Nigeria has many different cultures and ways of life', 'When Nigeria has only one big city', 'When people only sing one type of song', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1734, 21, 1, 'What does \"traditional attire\" refer to?', 'New clothes from another country', 'Clothes people wear for sports', 'Clothes that are part of a group\'s old customs and way of dressing', 'Clothes for sleeping', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1735, 21, 1, 'What does it mean to \"identify key characteristics of the Anang people\"?', 'To recognize and describe what makes them special', 'To guess what they are like', 'To draw a picture of them', 'To ignore their culture', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1736, 21, 1, 'Which of these is one of the ethnic groups mentioned in this lesson?', 'The Efik people', 'The French people', 'The Chinese people', 'The American people', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24');
INSERT INTO `exam_questions` (`question_id`, `subject_id`, `type`, `question`, `option1`, `option2`, `option3`, `option4`, `option5`, `feedback1`, `feedback2`, `feedback3`, `feedback4`, `feedback5`, `answer`, `marks`, `createdate`) VALUES
(1737, 21, 1, 'What is the traditional attire of the Fulani people often known for?', 'Very tight clothes', 'Only simple shirts', 'Only wearing shoes', 'Flowing robes and unique hats', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1738, 21, 1, 'What does cultural identity mean for a group of people?', 'When everyone in the group is exactly the same', 'The special way a group of people show who they are through their language, clothes, and customs', 'When people have no traditions', 'When people live in different houses', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1739, 21, 1, 'Which of these is a distinctive feature of the Ibibio language?', 'It has no sounds', 'It sounds exactly like English', 'It is a unique language with special tones and words', 'It is spoken by only one person', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1740, 21, 1, 'What does it mean to \"identify the traditional attire of the Efik people\"?', 'To recognize and name their special clothes', 'To ignore their clothes', 'To guess what they wear', 'To try to copy their clothes', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1741, 21, 1, 'What does it mean to be a hero or heroine?', 'Someone who performs brave acts and makes a positive impact on society', 'Someone who only cares about themselves', 'Someone who is very rich', 'Someone who is always strong physically', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1742, 21, 1, 'Which of these is a key contribution of Nigerian heroes and heroines?', 'They only built tall buildings', 'They were famous for singing', 'They only cared about their own families', 'They helped shape the country\'s history or development', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1743, 21, 1, 'What does cultural significance mean for a hero?', 'How famous they are', 'Their importance in representing and influencing a community\'s traditions or values', 'Their age', 'Their favorite food', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1744, 21, 1, 'Which of these is a region often associated with a Nigerian hero or heroine?', 'A foreign country', 'A specific part of Nigeria where they were born or did important work', 'A very cold place', 'An imaginary land', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1745, 21, 1, 'What does it mean to \"identify key Nigerian heroes and heroines\"?', 'To name and recognize important figures from Nigeria\'s past', 'To guess their names', 'To draw them', 'To ignore their stories', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1746, 21, 1, 'What is an ancient town?', 'A town that has been around for a very long time, with a rich history', 'A very new city', 'A town with no buildings', 'A town with only modern features', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1747, 21, 1, 'What does historical significance mean for an ancient town?', 'Its current population', 'Its size today', 'Its favorite food', 'Its importance in the past and how it shaped history', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1748, 21, 1, 'Which of these is a key feature of an ancient town?', 'Very tall skyscrapers', 'Old buildings, markets, or landmarks', 'Lots of new cars', 'Only modern shopping malls', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1749, 21, 1, 'What does it mean to \"identify key features of ancient towns\"?', 'To guess what old towns had', 'To only draw old towns', 'To name and describe important parts or qualities of old towns', 'To ignore old towns', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1750, 21, 1, 'What does \"cultural contributions\" refer to when discussing ancient towns?', 'How these towns added to Nigeria\'s traditions, art, or way of life', 'Only the food they ate', 'Only their old clothes', 'How much money they made', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1751, 21, 1, 'What is a modern town?', 'A town that has grown recently with new buildings, technologies, and services', 'A town that is very old', 'A town with no people', 'A town with only traditional customs', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1752, 21, 1, 'What does \"significance\" mean for modern towns?', 'How old they are', 'Their size in the past', 'Their traditional clothes', 'Their importance in today\'s world, often for jobs, business, or education', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1753, 21, 1, 'Which of these is a unique feature of many modern towns in Nigeria?', 'Only old mud houses', 'Tall buildings, shopping malls, and busy roads', 'Only traditional markets', 'No electricity', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1754, 21, 1, 'How do modern towns contribute to Nigeria\'s development?', 'By making people leave the country', 'By slowing down progress', 'By providing jobs, education, and services that help the country grow', 'By using only old ways', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1755, 21, 1, 'What does it mean to \"identify key modern towns\"?', 'To recognize and name important cities that have developed recently in Nigeria', 'To guess their names', 'To draw pictures of them', 'To ignore new towns', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:02:24'),
(1756, 21, 2, 'The Egun people are known for living near water and using special masks in their traditions. How does this help us recognize their unique traditions?', 'It means they don\'t like other places', 'It means their masks are new', 'It shows that their way of life and customs are connected to where they live', 'It only helps them swim', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1757, 21, 2, 'The Bura language has special sounds that are different from other Nigerian languages. How does this help us recognize their language features?', 'It means their language is old', 'It makes their language harder to learn', 'It means they don\'t talk much', 'It helps us hear what makes their language distinct and unique', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1758, 21, 2, 'Imagine a festival where people wear Anang traditional attire with special bright colors and patterns. How does this demonstrate comprehension of their culture?', 'It shows they like new clothes', 'It helps show off their unique cultural identity through their clothes', 'It means everyone must wear those clothes', 'It is only a party', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1759, 21, 2, 'Why is it important to learn about the different languages (like Anang, Bura, Egun) in Nigeria?', 'To help us understand and appreciate the many ways people communicate in Nigeria', 'So everyone can speak the same language', 'So we can make fun of other languages', 'It only helps linguists', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1760, 21, 2, 'You see a performance with traditional Egun dances and songs. How does this illustrate their unique culture?', 'It shows they are like everyone else', 'It showcases their unique artistic forms and ways of expressing their identity', 'It means the music is very loud', 'It is only for entertainment', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1761, 21, 2, 'The Efik people often wear a wrap-around cloth called a \"wrapper\" and a matching top. How does this attire express their cultural identity?', 'It shows they are like everyone else', 'It means they don\'t like modern clothes', 'It shows their unique style and traditional heritage through their clothing', 'It is only for parties', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1762, 21, 2, 'The Fulani language has specific words for different types of cattle. How does this feature of their language reflect their cultural identity?', 'It means they don\'t talk much', 'It is hard to learn', 'It is only about words', 'It shows how their language is shaped by their nomadic lifestyle and their connection to animals', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1763, 21, 2, 'You hear someone speaking a language with many clicking sounds. You learn this is the Ibibio language. How does this help you describe the distinctive features of the Ibibio language?', 'It means the language is noisy', 'It highlights how their language has unique sounds that make it special', 'It means the language is new', 'It is only for a few people', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1764, 21, 2, 'If a school organizes a \"Cultural Day\" where students wear traditional attire from different Nigerian groups, how does this activity appreciate the cultural diversity of Nigeria?', 'It helps students see and appreciate the beauty and variety of clothes and cultures across Nigeria', 'It makes everyone look the same', 'It makes the day longer', 'It is only about clothes', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1765, 21, 2, 'The Efik people are known for their rich oral traditions and storytelling in their language. How does this linguistic feature express their cultural identity?', 'It means they don\'t write', 'It shows how their language is used to pass down history, wisdom, and cultural stories', 'It makes their language silent', 'It is only about speaking', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1766, 21, 2, 'A Nigerian hero worked hard to bring clean water to their village. How does this action show their contribution to Nigeria\'s history?', 'It means they wanted to be rich', 'It only helped a few people', 'It improved the lives of many people and contributed to community development', 'It caused problems', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1767, 21, 2, 'A heroine always spoke out against unfair treatment. How does this action make them unique and show their legacy?', 'It made people dislike her', 'It made no difference', 'It only made her famous', 'It shows her courage and commitment to justice, inspiring others to fight for fairness', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1768, 21, 2, 'Imagine a hero from the Northern region who established a famous trading route. How does this connect them to their region and show their historical significance?', 'It means they liked trading', 'It shows how their actions in a specific region had a big impact on trade and growth', 'It means they never left their home', 'It is only a story', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1769, 21, 2, 'If you learn about a hero who promoted education for all children in their community. How does this discuss their contribution to Nigeria\'s history?', 'It highlights how their efforts helped spread knowledge and develop the country\'s future', 'It means schools were not important', 'It only helped boys', 'It made education harder', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1770, 21, 2, 'A problem-solving activity: \"How can we continue a hero\'s work in our community?\" How would you recognize the legacy of a historical figure who fought for peace?', 'By starting fights', 'By ignoring their message', 'By organizing activities that promote peace and understanding among peers', 'By only reading about them', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1771, 21, 2, 'The ancient city of Kano had very strong walls around it. How does this feature show its historical significance?', 'It made the city look pretty', 'It means the city was small', 'It protected the city during wars and shows its importance as a center of defense', 'It was only for decoration', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1772, 21, 2, 'Ile-Ife is known as the origin of the Yoruba people and has many ancient sculptures. How does this illustrate the cultural contributions of the town?', 'It means the town is only for artists', 'It means the town is new', 'It is only about the sculptures', 'It shows how the town is central to the Yoruba culture and their art', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1773, 21, 2, 'Compare Benin City with a modern city like Lagos. What is a unique characteristic that stands out about ancient Benin\'s influence on culture?', 'Benin City is bigger', 'Benin City is famous for its ancient bronze artworks and kingdom history', 'Lagos is older', 'Both are exactly the same', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1774, 21, 2, 'A problem-solving activity: \"How to learn about an ancient town that has few records.\" How would critical thinking skills help you?', 'You would look for clues in old stories, artifacts, or local customs', 'You would give up', 'You would guess the history', 'You would only read new books', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1775, 21, 2, 'The town of Calabar was an important trading port in the past. How did this influence Nigeria\'s history and culture?', 'It made trade stop', 'It connected Nigeria to other places, bringing new goods and ideas, and affecting local cultures', 'It only helped people who lived there', 'It meant people did not travel', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1776, 21, 2, 'Lagos has many tall buildings and a busy port. How does this feature show its significance in today\'s world?', 'It means Lagos is a small town', 'It means Lagos is a very old town', 'It highlights its role as a major center for business, trade, and modern life in Nigeria', 'It shows Lagos has no beaches', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1777, 21, 2, 'Abuja was built to be Nigeria\'s capital. How does this illustrate how a modern town contributes to Nigeria\'s development?', 'It makes the country smaller', 'It means the old capital was better', 'It only helps a few people', 'It provides a central hub for government, businesses, and services, helping the country grow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1778, 21, 2, 'You see new roads, hospitals, and schools being built in a town. How do these visual clues show the town is evolving and becoming modern?', 'It means the town is shrinking', 'These are signs of growth and development, bringing new services and opportunities', 'It shows the town is very old', 'It means people are leaving the town', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1779, 21, 2, 'Why are modern towns important for economic growth?', 'They provide jobs, places for businesses, and markets for goods, helping the economy grow', 'They only use old ideas', 'They make money disappear', 'They only help rich people', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1780, 21, 2, 'A problem-solving activity: \"How to make a modern town cleaner.\" How would you apply knowledge of town features to propose a solution?', 'Blame the citizens', 'Suggest adding more waste bins, organizing recycling programs, and promoting environmental awareness', 'Ignore the trash', 'Only clean one street', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:03:19'),
(1781, 21, 3, 'Your class is discussing cultural diversity. Which statement best evaluates why understanding different ethnic groups helps build a stronger Nigeria?', 'Everyone should be the same for unity.', 'Understanding differences causes problems.', 'It helps people respect and learn from each other, making Nigeria richer and more united.', 'Only one culture is important.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:04:11'),
(1782, 21, 3, 'If you were asked to create a drawing to show what makes the Anang people unique, what key characteristic would you highlight?', 'Their modern houses', 'Their favorite type of car', 'Their school building', 'Their traditional clothing patterns or a famous craft they make', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:04:11'),
