(1862, 22, 3, 'Your class is discussing making good choices. Which statement best evaluates why social skills (like good communication) are crucial for avoiding criminal behaviors?', 'Social skills are only for talking.', 'Social skills make choices harder.', 'They help you avoid arguments and make friends with good influences, reducing negative interactions.', 'Criminal behavior is not affected by social skills.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:09:16'),
(1863, 22, 3, 'If you were asked to create a school campaign on \"Making Positive Decisions,\" what key message would you emphasize about resisting peer pressure?', 'Always agree with friends.', 'Its okay to do what others do sometimes.', 'Dont tell anyone about peer pressure.', 'Your choices are your own, choose wisely, say no to bad pressure.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:09:16'),
