(1867, 22, 3, 'Think about the role of empathy in community safety. If you had to design a role-play scenario where students practice effective communication with a trusted adult after seeing a problem, what would be the most important part of the conversation?', 'How loud they can talk.', 'How quickly they can run away.', 'How they clearly describe the problem and their feelings about it.', 'How much they can hide.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:09:16'),
(1868, 22, 3, 'Your class is discussing the role of emotional intelligence in security. Which statement best evaluates why managing your own emotions is crucial for personal safety?', 'Emotions have no impact on safety.', 'Only strong people can control emotions.', 'Controlling emotions helps you stay calm and think clearly in dangerous situations, making safer choices.', 'Its okay to panic.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:09:16'),
