(1870, 22, 3, 'Think about applying self-awareness and self-regulation techniques to stay safe. If you had to design a \"Feeling Safe\" activity for younger students, what would be the most important task for them to demonstrate?', 'How to make others angry.', 'How to make noise.', 'How to ignore their feelings.', 'How to recognize when they feel unsafe and how to calm themselves down to think clearly.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:09:16'),
