(1919, 13, 2, 'Imagine a child sees someone drop their groceries and helps pick them up. How does this demonstrate heroism in their daily life?', 'It shows they are very strong.', 'It means they want a reward.', 'It\'s a small act of kindness that shows bravery and a willingness to help.', 'It means they like groceries.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
