(1921, 13, 2, 'A hero makes a difficult choice to tell the truth, even if it gets them into trouble. How does this action reflect their qualities?', 'It shows they are afraid.', 'It highlights their honesty and bravery in a tough situation.', 'It proves they don\'t care about others.', 'It means they are not smart.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
