(1923, 13, 2, 'A Nigerian hero helped unite different groups of people. How did this impact Nigerian society?', 'It caused more arguments.', 'It helped people live together more peacefully and work towards common goals.', 'It made people dislike each other.', 'It made the country weaker.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
(1924, 13, 2, 'You attend a traditional marriage where the groom\'s family brings gifts like yams and palm wine. How does this explain the meaning of objects used in the ceremony?', 'It shows they have a lot of food.', 'It means they are just bringing presents.', 'These gifts often show respect, blessings, and commitment between the two families.', 'It means they are eating a big meal.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
