(1926, 13, 2, 'Your community has different ways of celebrating marriages, some with lots of drumming, others with quiet blessings. How does this show the diversity of marital practices?', 'It means people are arguing.', 'It highlights that different groups have unique and special ways of celebrating marriage.', 'It means everyone is the same.', 'It only helps one group.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
