(1928, 13, 2, 'A marriage involves many family members from different towns coming together. How does this illustrate its importance to families and communities?', 'It shows that people like to travel.', 'It demonstrates how marriage brings families and communities closer and creates new bonds.', 'It means the community is very big.', 'It is only for a party.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
