(1930, 13, 2, 'A couple chooses to get married in a court registry. How does this way of getting married differ from a traditional or church wedding?', 'It is always louder.', 'It has many more guests.', 'It is only for famous people.', 'It is a legal marriage that does not involve religious or cultural ceremonies.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
