(1932, 13, 2, 'If a marriage ceremony includes a lot of singing, dancing, and special family rituals, how does this explain the cultural importance of marriage traditions in Nigeria?', 'It means the ceremony is very long.', 'It shows that the families are rich.', 'It demonstrates how marriage is a joyous event deeply rooted in a community\'s customs and shared identity.', 'It is only for fun.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
(1933, 13, 2, 'A wedding gown is worn by the bride in a church wedding. What does this object symbolize?', 'That the bride likes white.', 'Purity, new beginnings, and celebration for the bride.', 'That the dress is expensive.', 'That the bride will leave.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
(1934, 13, 2, 'You have a headache. How does taking painkillers correctly (as told by a parent) show the importance of taking medicine properly?', 'It means you can take any medicine.', 'It makes the headache worse.', 'It ensures the medicine works safely and effectively to relieve pain.', 'It only helps for a short time.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
(1935, 13, 2, 'A child is given traditional herbs by their grandparent for a cough. How does this illustrate who the right people are to administer medicines?', 'It shows anyone can give medicine.', 'It means the child will get sicker.', 'It means the herbs are from a doctor.', 'It shows that trusted family members with traditional knowledge can also administer certain medicines.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
(1936, 13, 2, 'Someone takes a medicine that is not theirs and feels very sick. How does this recognize the dangers of drug abuse?', 'It shows the medicine is weak.', 'It demonstrates that taking medicine incorrectly or without permission can cause serious harm.', 'It means they will get better quickly.', 'It is only a small problem.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
(1937, 13, 2, 'If a doctor gives you medicine for a fever, how does their role explain who the right person is to give medicine?', 'Doctors are trained to know the right medicine and dosage for different illnesses.', 'Doctors only give medicine to sick people.', 'Doctors like giving medicine.', 'Anyone can give medicine if a doctor writes it.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
(1938, 13, 2, 'A situation is given: \"You find an old bottle of medicine under the sink.\" How would you apply knowledge of medicine safety?', 'Drink it to see what it tastes like.', 'Show it to a trusted adult and ask what it is, not touching it yourself.', 'Throw it in the trash without telling anyone.', 'Keep it as a toy.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
