(1941, 13, 2, 'You learn that drug abuse can lead to increased crime in a community. How does this effect impact the community?', 'It makes the community safer.', 'It means people will have more jobs.', 'It creates insecurity and breaks down trust among community members.', 'It makes the community richer.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3', 0, '2025-07-01 14:15:09'),
