(3095, 36, 3, 'You are aspiring to be a playwright. Why is it important to pay attention to \"stage directions\" and \"transitions\" when writing your script?', 'They are only for the director to worry about.', 'They are only for historical plays.', 'They make the play longer unnecessarily.', 'They help to guide the actors and crew.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '4', 0, '2025-07-14 12:54:59'),
(3096, 36, 3, 'You are directing a play. How would you ensure that the various creative aspects, such as acting, set design, and lighting, blend together seamlessly to tell the story effectively?', 'By providing clear guidance, feedback, and coordinating rehearsals to ensure all elements support the director\'s overall vision for the production.', 'By letting each department work completely independently.', 'By only focusing on the actors and ignoring everything else.', 'By making sure all elements contradict each other.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', 0, '2025-07-14 12:54:59'),
