(170, 11, 4, 'Lesson 2', '', 'Big Question: Why do we need others in our lives?\n\n\r\nLearning Objectives:\n\r\n1. Define interdependence.\n\r\n2. Identify people we depend on and why (family, teachers, doctors, etc.).\n\r\n3. Understand mutual support and cooperation.\n\r\n4. Act out interdependence scenarios to demonstrate understanding.', '<b>Interdependence</b>: Depending on each other for support and help\n<b>Community</b>: A group of people living together in one area\n<b>Cooperation</b>: Working together to reach a goal\n<b>Support</b>: Giving help when needed\n<b>Mutual</b>: Shared between two or more people', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fQS5Yu9UdkM', '2025-05-25 22:29:48'),
(171, 11, 4, 'Lesson 3', '', 'Big Question: What does it mean to be part of a family?\n\n\r\nLearning Objectives:\n\r\n1. Define what a family is and identify types (nuclear, extended).\n\r\n2. Understand roles and responsibilities within a family.\n\r\n3. Describe how families provide love, support, and guidance.\n\r\n4. Create a family chart or storybook to describe their own family.', '<b>Family</b>: A group of people related by blood or love\n<b>Parents</b>: The people who raise children\n<b>Siblings</b>: Brothers and sisters\n<b>Respect</b>: Treating someone with care and kindness\n<b>Responsibility</b>: Being dependable and doing your duties', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6RNzDjtG1t8', '2025-05-25 22:29:48'),
